55
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:00,600
[SPEAKER_03] Puno toga je zabranjeno.

56
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:03,600
[SPEAKER_03] Da, ali vidiš, zato sam te zvao u ovo vrijeme.

57
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:06,600
