59
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:13,600
[SPEAKER_03] Na primjer knjiga Postanka.

60
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:16,600
[SPEAKER_03] Pričat ćemo danas puno o njoj.

61
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:20,600
[SPEAKER_03] Odnosno o toj poveznici judaizma i hršćanstva.

62
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:22,600
[SPEAKER_03] Zapravo u tim dodajnim točkama.

63
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:24,600
[SPEAKER_03] Prima što pređemo na to,

64
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:26,600
