111
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:30,600
[SPEAKER_03] Na određeno radno vrijeme.

112
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:31,600
[SPEAKER_03] Da.

113
00:12:31,600 --> 00:12:34,600
